OL,3,CCouncil takes back control of some
OL,4,Csport services from charity
OL,6,FITV Border's Isla Todd went to the
OL,7,Fmeeting to hear about the future of
OL,8,FLive Borders
OL,10,FScottish Borders Council is taking
OL,11,Fback control of some sport services
OL,12,Ffrom Live Borders, the charity
OL,13,Fdelivering sport, leisure and cultural
OL,14,Fservices on the authority's behalf.
OL,16,FThe council have set a deadline of the
OL,17,Fend of September to regain control of
OL,18,Fthe services.
