OL,3,CCouncil takes back control of some
OL,4,Csport services from charity
OL,6,FThe charity has been experiencing
OL,7,Ffinancial problems since the Covid
OL,8,Fpandemic.
OL,10,FAt a meeting on 27 July 2024, elected
OL,11,Fmembers decided that the Active
OL,12,FSchools and sports development
OL,13,Fservices will return under council
OL,14,Fcontrol.
OL,16,FA further report in September will
OL,17,Flook at the future of cultural
OL,18,Ffacilities like libraries, museums,
OL,19,Fand visitor attractions.
