OL,6,FThe return of all services to the
OL,7,Fcouncil was also considered.
OL,9,FAlison Moore, chair of Live Borders,
OL,10,Fadded: "I and my fellow Trustees
OL,11,Faccept today's decision by elected
OL,12,Fmembers to seek to change the
OL,13,Fgovernance of Live Borders
OL,15,F"We will work with Council colleagues
OL,16,Fto ensure that this transition is
OL,17,Forderly and takes place as quickly as
OL,18,Fpossible.
