OL,6,F"The Trust remains firmly committed to
OL,7,Fdelivering on our vision of supporting
OL,8,Fa healthier, happier and stronger
OL,9,FScottish Borders."
OL,11,FLive Borders has been operating since
OL,12,F2016 but in the last few years has
OL,13,Fexperienced financial issues, relying
OL,14,Fon handouts from SBC to keep it afloat.
OL,16,FThe charity has faced unprecedented
OL,17,Fchallenges, including the Covid
OL,18,Fpandemic, cost of living and changes
OL,19,Fin customer trends.
